"title": "8792: oppression, God's attitude to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8792: oppression, god's attitude to",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God is concerned for the victims of oppression; he hears, sustains and delivers them. Christians are to exhibit the same concern.</p>\n<h2>God forbids the oppression of the poor and vulnerable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:10\">ZEC 7:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:22-Prov22:23\">PRO 22:22–22:23</a></p>\n<h2>God warns the oppressor</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:5-Jer7:7\">JER 7:5–7:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:14-Isa33:15\">ISA 33:14–33:15</a></p>\n<h2>God condemns the oppressor</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:4\">PSA 72:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:1-Isa10:3\">ISA 10:1–10:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:5\">PRO 17:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:12-Isa30:13\">ISA 30:12–30:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:7\">EZK 22:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:13\">EZK 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:31\">EZK 22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6\">AMO 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:11\">AMO 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1-Mic2:3\">MIC 2:1–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:1\">NAM 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:19\">NAM 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a></p>\n<h2>God's concern for the oppressed</h2>\n<h3>Showing mercy to the oppressed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:6\">PSA 103:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:18\">DEU 10:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:8\">1SA 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:7-Ps146:9\">PSA 146:7–146:9</a></p>\n<h3>Defending the oppressed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:4\">PSA 72:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:18\">DEU 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:9\">PSA 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:17-Ps10:18\">PSA 10:17–10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:5\">PSA 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:5\">PSA 68:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:7-Ps146:9\">PSA 146:7–146:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:33-Jer50:34\">JER 50:33–50:34</a></p>\n<h3>Delivering the oppressed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:15\">JOB 5:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:7-Exod3:9\">EXO 3:7–3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:21\">DEU 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:10\">PSA 35:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:6\">PSA 107:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:13\">PSA 107:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:19\">PSA 107:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:22\">PRO 20:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:3-Isa14:4\">ISA 14:3–14:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:26\">ISA 49:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:34\">ACT 7:34</a></p>\n<h2>The oppressed turn to the LORD</h2>\n<h3>In prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:12\">PSA 10:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:3\">JDG 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:9-Judg10:10\">JDG 10:9–10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:38-2Chr6:39\">2CH 6:38–6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:9\">PSA 42:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:1\">PSA 57:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:11\">PSA 79:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3-Ps82:4\">PSA 82:3–82:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:1-Ps94:7\">PSA 94:1–94:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:10\">REV 6:10</a></p>\n<h3>In trust</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25\">ACT 16:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25\">JOB 19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:1-Ps42:3\">PSA 42:1–42:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:7\">PSA 138:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17\">2CO 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:4-2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:4–6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:19</a></p>\n<h2>Christian attitudes towards the oppressed</h2>\n<h3>Showing practical mercy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:7\">MAT 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:10\">LEV 19:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:19-Deut24:21\">DEU 24:19–24:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:8-Prov31:9\">PRO 31:8–31:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:20\">PRO 31:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:9-Isa58:10\">ISA 58:9–58:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:3\">JER 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:9\">ZEC 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:3\">MAT 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:39\">MAT 25:34–25:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">ROM 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:10\">PHP 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:15\">PHP 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h3>Showing concern</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:3\">HEB 13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:15\">ROM 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:2\">GAL 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:18\">COL 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:10\">PHM 1:10</a></p>",
